新建领地--/tty add 领地边角坐标1 领地边角坐标2\n新建子领地--/:
Create territory -- /tty add territory corner coordinate1 territory corner coordinate2
Create sub territory -- /tty add_sub sub territory corner coordinate1 sub territory corner coordinate2
List territory -- /tty list
Delete territory -- /tty del territory name
Rename territory -- /tty rename old territory name new territory name
Set territory permissions -- /tty set permission name (if_jiaohu|if_break|if_tp|if_build|if_bomb|if_damage) permission value territory name
Set territory administrator -- /tty manager add|remove (add|remove) player name territory name
Set territory member -- /tty member add|remove (add|remove) player name territory name
Set territory teleport point -- /tty settp territory teleport coordinate territory name
Teleport to territory -- /tty tp territory name
